The Design Lions celebrate visual craftsmanship. Entries need to demonstrate how design has been used to define a brand or communicate its key messages. It's all about work where a unique visual identity leads to consumer recognition or understanding. #CannesLions2017: Design shortlistThe Cannes Lions Design shortlist has been released, with five SA campaigns making the cut...1 day ago Bronze Lions were awarded for the following SA work:TBWA/Hunt/Lascaris JHB for Goodbye Malaria&#x2019;s Beautiful Pathogens (Illustration: Packaging)OpenCo JHB for Soweto Gold 76 Marked by Bravery (Special Editions & Promotional Packaging)GRID WW JHB was also mentioned with TBWA/Chiat/Day LA for TBWA Identity Refresh TBWA Hunt Lascaris' 'Beautiful Pathogens'. OpenCo's 'Marked by Bravery'. TBWA Identity Refresh. The Grand Prix then went to AP Thailand and CJ Worx Bangkok for AP Public Company Ltd&#x2019;s Property Development work, &#x2018;The Unusual Football Field&#x2019;. The work was hailed for transforming small spaces into fun public ones. View the full table of winning work below: Design Lions Winners EntrantTitleClientProductAwardAP THAILAND, Bangkok / CJ WORX, BangkokTHE UNUSUAL FOOTBALL FIELDAP (THAILAND) PUBLIC COMPANY LIMITED.PROPERTY DEVELOPMENTGrand Prix OGILVY NEW YORKTHE REFUGEE NATIONAMNESTY INTERNATIONALAWARNESS AROUND THE REFUGEE CAUSEGold LionDDB GROUP GERMANY, BerlinWORDS OF WELCOMEVEREIN F R BERLINER STADTMISSIONTAPE ROLLGold LionVML, Kansas CityWELCOME TO MY NEIGHBORHOODYOUTH AMBASSADORSNON-PROFIT ORGANIZATIONGold LionLEO BURNETT TORONTOIKEA: COOK THIS PAGEIKEA CANADAIKEA CANADAGold LionPEREIRA & O'DELL, San FranciscoWRITING OUR RIGHTS: THE EMPOWERMENT WORKBOOKIGNITEIGNITEGold LionCLEMENGER BBDO MELBOURNEMEET GRAHAMTRANSPORT ACCIDENT COMMISSION VICTORIATRANSPORT ACCIDENT COMMISSION VICTORIAGold LionY&R DUBAIONE BOOK FOR PEACEINTERRELIGIOUS COUNCIL OF BOSNIA AND HERZEGOVINAINTERRELIGIOUS COUNCIL OF BOSNIA AND HERZEGOVINAGold LionLEO BURNETT MELBOURNEREWORDHEADSPAC